{
  "texts": [
    "Note that Google DeepMind has only shared very limited information about its AGI Safety Council, so its precise mandate remains opaque.",
    "A purpose trust is a special type of trust which exists to advance some non-charitable purpose.",
    "Unlike other trusts, it has no beneficiaries.",
    "We wish to emphasize that there are substantial differences between jurisdictions.",
    "It is therefore difficult to make any conclusive statements about the enforceability of decisions."
  ]
}